(POWERED SHOPPING - USER INTERFACE INTERACTION GUIDE) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Generated on: 2026-04-20) Tj
T*
(Audience: End users and demo reviewers) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. WHAT THIS APP IS FOR) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Powered Shopping is a voice-enabled shopping interface where you can:) Tj
T*
(-  sign in) Tj
T*
(-  search products by typing or voice) Tj
T*
(-  add/remove items in cart) Tj
T*
(-  ask for recommendations) Tj
T*
(-  complete checkout in guided steps) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(You can use it in two ways:) Tj
T*
(-  Voice-first mode \(speak commands\)) Tj
T*
(-  Manual mode \(type commands and use on-screen buttons\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. USER JOURNEY AT A GLANCE) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.  Open app and sign in \(Email/Password or Google\).) Tj
T*
(2.  Land on dashboard with navigation menu and live status chips.) Tj
T*
(3.  Browse products in Shop view or use Voice Copilot.) Tj
T*
(4.  Add items to cart from product cards or commands.) Tj
T*
(5.  Open Checkout and complete 3-step flow.) Tj
T*
(6.  Place order and continue shopping.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3. LOGIN SCREEN \(AUTH\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(What user sees:) Tj
T*
(-  Login/Sign Up tabs) Tj
T*
(-  Email and Password fields) Tj
T*
(-  Continue with Google button) Tj
T*
(-  Theme toggle \(Light/Dark\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(How user interacts:) Tj
T*
(-  Choose `Login` if account exists, or `Sign Up` for new account.) Tj
T*
(-  Enter credentials and submit.) Tj
T*
(-  On success, dashboard opens.) Tj
T*
(-  On failure, error message appears on same screen.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4. MAIN DASHBOARD LAYOUT) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(After login, the interface has these zones:) Tj
T*
(-  Left sidebar navigation) Tj
T*
(-  Top status bar) Tj
T*
(-  Main content area \(changes by selected view\)) Tj
T*
(-  Optional floating buttons \(`AI` and `Mic`\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
ET
endstream
