T*
(12. FALLBACK BEHAVIOR USERS SHOULD KNOW) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(To keep experience stable, interface auto-falls back when a service is down:) Tj
T*
(-  If live catalog fails: backup catalog is used.) Tj
T*
(-  If browser speech recognition fails: fallback recorder is available.) Tj
T*
(-  If AI assistant mode fails: deterministic command parser handles common commands.) Tj
T*
(-  If cloud cart storage is unavailable: cart runs in temporary local memory mode.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(From user perspective, app still works with minor feature limitations.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(13. MOBILE INTERACTION NOTES) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(-  Sidebar opens with `Menu` button.) Tj
T*
(-  Floating `AI` and `Mic` buttons give quick access.) Tj
T*
(-  Core flows \(search, add, cart, checkout\) are available on mobile and desktop.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(14. QUICK FIRST-TIME USER SCRIPT \(DEMO READY\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1.  Login with email/password.) Tj
T*
(2.  Open `Catalog AI`.) Tj
T*
(3.  Say: "Show sneakers under 3000".) Tj
T*
(4.  Add one item using card button.) Tj
T*
(5.  Open cart and remove one item.) Tj
T*
(6.  Go to checkout and complete all 3 steps.) Tj
T*
(7.  Place order and show confirmation screen.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
